data.description: Here is a very affordable home in Pueblo, ready for new owners to make it their own. Come see the xeriscaped front yard and the oversized backyard ready for all your summer barbecues. The 2 beds, and 1 bath are all on one level making for seamless upkeep. An aluminum ramp provides great accessibility for anyone. Schedule a tour today!
